---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import hero from "../../public/img/hero.svg";
---

<section>
    <div class="px-12 mx-auto max-w-screen-2xl lg:py-52">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center mx-auto lg:gap-8">
            <div class="mt-16 w-full lg:max-w-lg lg:w-1/2 rounded-xl lg:mt-0">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
                    <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg">
                        <div
                            class="absolute top-0 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 -right-4  w-56 h-56 mix-blend-lighten filter blur-[75px] opacity-70 lg:blur-[150px] lg:-right-14"
                        >
                        </div>

                        <div
                            class="absolute rounded-full bg-emerald-400 -bottom-8 right-28 w-56 h-56 mix-blend-lighten filter blur-[75px] opacity-70 lg:blur-[150px] lg:right-60"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div class="max-w-full flex justify-center items-center">
                            <Image class="drop-shadow-xl max-w-80 lg:max-w-md" src={hero} alt="hero"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex flex-col items-center mt-12 text-center lg:flex-grow lg:max-w-3xl lg:mb-0 lg:mt-0 lg:items-start lg:text-left"
            >
                <span class="mb-8 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-blue-500 uppercase lg:mt-20">
                    Inspira, Conecta, Destaca
                </span>
                <h1
                    class="mb-8 text-4xl font-bold text-white lg:text-6xl"
                >
                    ¡Tu Página Web, Tu Estilo, <br>Nuestro Arte!
                </h1>
                <p class="mb-8 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-400">
                    Explora cómo nuestro enfoque personalizado y experiencia en desarrollo web pueden llevar tu negocio <br class="hidden lg:block">al siguiente nivel.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>